videos.description: Asia Durr near the middle of the floor finds Mariya Moore who assists Myisha Hines-Allen in a play that shows Louisville's great ball movement.
videos.headline: Louisville's Durr moves ball well and Hines-Allen finishes with lay-in

videos.description: Mariya Moore from outside the arc, drives past two defenders and scores.
videos.headline: Louisville's Moore drives past two defenders and banks it in off glass

videos.description: Marina Mabrey adds 3 for the Fighting Irish with a beautiful shot from the wing
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Mabrey knocks down a 3-pointer from the wing

videos.description: Off the break away, Marina Mabrey gets the dime at the other end of the floor to score and one!
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Allen sends half court pass to Mabrey who scores and one

videos.description: Asia Durr knocks down a 3-pointer at the 3rd quarter buzzer.
videos.headline: Louisville's Durr knocks down a step back 3-pointer at the buzzer

videos.description: Jackie Young extends lead for Notre Dame with 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Young knocks down a catch and shoot 3-pointer with one second on the shot clock

videos.description: Post-game Breakdown: Notre Dame defeats Louisville 84-73 in ACC Women's Semifinal
videos.headline: Fighting Irish defeat Louisville in ACC Women's Semifinal
